## Summary

This bot provides a fully automated framework to keep a constant 2Ã— leveraged futures position on BTCUSDT. It combines margin and leverage controls, position rebalancing logic, live price streaming, and a FastAPI interface for easy monitoring and control. Feel free to extend it with custom trading logic, error handling, or persistence layers to suit your production needs.

## Setup Code

```
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install "fastapi[standard]"
touch main.py
fastapi dev main.py
```

